1. Ni tao thu 5 cai IP nhung chua lam thanh IP duoc, ko biet sao. 
Mi lam thu nha. 
Lam duoc thi file top chi can add 5 cai IP la xong.
(ip_repo)


ChatGPT Huong dan:

Step 4: Register Your IP in Platform Designer
-Open Platform Designer in Quartus
-Go to Tools → Options → IP Catalog Search Locations
-Click Add... and choose the ip_repo/ folder
-Click Rescan Repositories
-Now, in the IP list, you’ll see Adder IP (No Avalon) under Custom IP

Step 5: Use Your IP
-Drag Adder IP (No Avalon) into your Platform Designer system.
-You'll see a conduit interface with ports a, b, sum.
-Connect those ports to another component or export them (right-click → Export Signal).
-Generate the HDL system normally (click Generate HDL).
-In Quartus, make sure to:
  -Add the generated HDL files and your VHDL (adder_ip.vhd) to the project.


2. Ni tao thu file Top de noi 5 khoi lai voi nhau (top_file/top.vhd)


P/S: common/inoutput_types.vhd giong khai bao struct trong C vay ah.
Moi khi thang Cross Bar thay doi chan In/Out (cuar Data), Mi chi can thay doi trong do thoi.
Luu y: Dang de in/out cau truc giong nhau, neu khac nhau Mi phai tach ra thanh 2 cai record (HDL goi la record, giong struct)
